    Typical location: C:\Program Files\SOLIDWORKS Corp\SOLIDWORKS\
    
    Required DLLs:
    - SolidWorks.Interop.sldworks.dll
    - SolidWorks.Interop.swconst.dll
    - SolidWorks.Interop.swpublished.dll
    
    To add: Project > Add Reference > Browse > Navigate to SOLIDWORKS installation
